{
  "stem": "150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Look, from the point of view of a kid, it was very boring.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The adults would go to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The kids would stay behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was really nothing for us to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From time to time, there were Aktions, when they would come and search through the ghetto, and they would take people out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or they would surround an area of the ghetto and, you know, sort the people out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or they would go through the entire ghetto looking for children or old people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came and burned down the hospital that we had a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in between the Aktions, which were totally unpredictable, as a kid, it was really very boring.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to find things to do because days were long.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we played a lot of soccer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- you know, you would go out on the field and try and pick up a team.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'd say, hey, where's Joey?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somebody would say, oh, Joey, didn't you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took him away last Wednesday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'd say, oh, yeah, what a shame.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a good center forward.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now we have to find somebody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We'd go to the houses where the people had been taken away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the-- the Jewish authority, they had carts that would go to the place-- to the houses of the people who had been taken away in the previous Aktion.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would take all the belongings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would be taken to a large warehouse and sorted out, and it would be distributed among the people who needed it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But before the Jewish authority could get it, we, the kids, would go to those houses-- to the houses and search through them and look for books to have something to read.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
